# BMGD Framework

This project uses the Unreal Companion Studio for AI-assisted game development.

## Quick Start

1. **Read the project index**: `.unreal-companion/COMPANION.md`
2. **Check current tasks**: `.unreal-companion/docs/.companion/tasks.json`
3. **Adopt an agent** for specialized help

## Agents

Reference agents with `@bmgd/agents/{name}`:

- **game-dev** - Implementation, coding, debugging
- **game-designer** - Mechanics, balance, player experience  
- **game-architect** - Technical architecture, systems design
- **game-qa** - Testing, quality, bug tracking

## Workflows

Reference workflows with `@bmgd/workflows/{name}`:

- **quick-prototype** (5 min) - Define a game idea rapidly
- **game-brief** (30 min) - Complete game brief document
- **gdd** (1-2h) - Full Game Design Document
- **game-architecture** - Technical architecture design

## Directory Structure

```
