│   ├── design/           # GDD, mechanics
│   ├── technical/        # Architecture, specs
│   ├── production/       # Sprints, planning
│   └── .companion/
│       └── tasks.json    # Task board
└── .cursor/rules/bmgd/   # This folder
```

## Creating Documents

When creating docs:
1. Use the appropriate folder (concept/, design/, technical/, production/)
2. Use markdown format
3. Update COMPANION.md after creating important documents

